msgctxt "#30605"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko te tau hei timata te tatau i nga hongere mai. Ka whakamahia anake ina [B]Whakamahia nga nama hongere tuara[/B] mai i nga tautuhinga PVR ka whakahohea, karekau he nama hongere e tukuna i roto i te konae M3U."

#. help: Channels - oneRadioGroup
#. help: Channels - twoRadioGroup
#. help: Channels - threeRadioGroup
#. help: Channels - fourRadioGroup
#. help: Channels - fiveRadioGroup
msgctxt "#30606"
msgid ""
msgstr "Kaua e aro ki nga tohu 'tvg-chno' me nga hongere nama anake ma te ota i te M3U timata mai i te 'Tīmata tau hongere'."

#. help: Channels - customTvGroupsFile
msgctxt "#30610"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko nga hongere pouaka whakaata anake no nga roopu (arā, he huanga [B]group-title[/B]) ka utaina mai i te konae M3U."

#. help: Channels - customRadioGroupsFile
msgctxt "#30611"
msgid ""
msgstr "Kōwhiria mai i tetahi o nga momo e toru e whai ake nei: [B]Nga roopu katoa[/B] Utaina nga roopu pouaka whakaata katoa mai i te konae M3U; [B]Etahi roopu[/B] Me utaina nga roopu kua tohua ki nga whiringa ka whai ake; [B]Nga roopu ritenga[/B] Utaina he huinga roopu mai i te konae M3U kua utaina nga ingoa mai i te konae XML."

#. help: Channels - numTvGroups
msgctxt "#30612"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mēnā kua tautuhia te kōwhiringa o mua ki 'Etahi rōpū' me whakapūtā koe he rōpū pouaka whakaata kia utaina mai i te kōnae M3U. Kia mahara ko tenei te ingoa roopu e whakaatuhia ana i te huanga taitara-rōpū (arā, 'UK (TV)'). He pū tairongo tēnei tautuhinga."

#. help: Channels - numRadioGroups
msgctxt "#30614"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mēnā kua tautuhia te kōwhiringa o mua ki 'Etahi rōpū' me whakapūtā he rōpū reo irirangi hei tiki mai i te kōnae M3U. Tena koa, koinei te ingoa roopu e whakaatuhia ana i te huanga taitara-rōpū (arā, 'UK (Irirangi)'). He pū tairongo tēnei tautuhinga."

#. help: General - radioChannelGroupsOnly
msgctxt "#30615"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko te konae i whakamahia hei uta i nga roopu TV ritenga. Ko te kōnae taunoa ko `customTVGroups-example.xml`."

#. help info - EPG Settings
#. help-category: EPG Settings
msgctxt "#30616"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko te konae i whakamahia hei uta i nga roopu Irirangi ritenga. Ko te kōnae taunoa ko `customRadioGroups-example.xml`."

#. help: EPG Settings - epgTimeShift
msgctxt "#30617"
msgid ""
msgstr "Te maha o nga roopu pouaka whakaata hei uta ina ko `Some groups` te aratau kua tohua. Tae atu ki te 5 ka taea te kowhiri. Mēnā neke atu i te 5 e hiahiatia ana me whakamahi kē te aratau 'Rōpū Ritenga'."

#. help: EPG Settings - epgTSOverside
msgctxt "#30618"
msgid ""
msgstr "Te maha o nga roopu reo irirangi hei uta ina ko `Some groups` te aratau kua tohua. Tae atu ki te 5 ka taea te kowhiri. Mēnā neke atu i te 5 e hiahiatia ana me whakamahi kē te aratau 'Rōpū Ritenga'."

#. help: EPG Settings - epgIgnoreCaseForChannelIds
msgctxt "#30619"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko nga hongere reo irirangi anake no nga roopu (arā, he huanga [B]group-title[/B]) ka utaina mai i te konae M3U."

# empty strings from id 30627 to 30639
#. help info - Channel Logos
#. help-category: Channel Logos
msgctxt "#30620"
msgid ""
msgstr "Nga tautuhinga e pa ana ki te EPG. Kia mahara ka utaina e Kodi nga raraunga EPG ina hiahia ana. Ko te taapiri ka kaha te utaina o nga raraunga EPG ahakoa te tono a Kodi mena ka taea te hopu, ka hiahiatia ranei nga tohu XMLTV."

#. help: EPG Settings - connectionCheckIntervalSecs
msgctxt "#30625"
msgid ""
msgstr "Whakaritehia nga wa EPG ma tenei uara, mai i te -12 haora ki te +14 haora."

#. help-category: Channel Logos
msgctxt "#30626"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mena ka whakakorehia te nekehanga wa mo nga hongere katoa me `EPG time shift`. Ki te kore e whakahohea `EPG time shift` me te nuku wa takitahi mo ia hongere (mena e waatea ana) ka whakamahia."

#. help: Channel Logos - logoFromEpg
msgctxt "#30627"
msgid ""
msgstr "Kaua e aro ki te keehi mo nga EPG Channel ID, e mohiotia ana ko tvg-id's, ina taurite nga hongere ki nga urunga EPG. Mena ka monokia, ka whakamahia te whakahoatanga kirihipi anake."

#. help: Genres - useEpgGenreText
msgctxt "#30628"
msgid ""
msgstr "I te wa e tirotirohia ana mo te konae M3U whaimana, te roa o te wa tatari i mua i te whakamutu i te nganatanga."

#. help: Genres - genresPathType
msgctxt "#30629"
msgid ""
msgstr "I te wa e tirotiro ana mo te konae M3U whaimana, te roa o te wa tatari i waenga i nga nganatanga. Kia mahara ko tetahi konae whaimana ka tirohia i te tiimatanga ka kitea he konae whaimana ka mutu nga arowhai."

#. help: Genres - genresPath
msgctxt "#30640"
msgid ""
msgstr "Tautuhinga e pa ana ki nga Moko Channel."

#. help: Genres - genresUrl
msgctxt "#30644"
msgid ""
msgstr "Te manakohanga me pehea te hapai i nga waitohu hongere. Ko nga whiringa ko: [B]Kaua[/B] - Kaua e whakamahi i nga waitohu hongere mai i te konae XMLTV; [B]Me pai ake ki a M3U[/B] - Whakamahia te moko hongere mai i te M3U mena e waatea ana whakamahia te tohu XMLTV; [B]Me pai ake te XMLTV[/B] - Whakamahia te moko hongere mai i te konae XMLTV mena e waatea ana whakamahia te tohu M3U."

# empty strings from id 30665 to 30679
#. help info - Advanced
#. help-category: Advanced
msgctxt "#30661"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ki te whakahohea, ka whakamahia he konae mapi momo ki te tiki momo momo me te momo iti ka whakamahi i te momo tuhinga a te EPG (arā, te kuputuhi 'kāwai') mo te momo, kaua ki te kuputuhi taunoa kodi."

#. help: Advanced - transformMulticastStreamUrls
msgctxt "#30662"
msgid ""
msgstr "Tīpakohia te waahi ka kitea nga momo rauemi XML. Ko nga whiringa ko: [B]Ara rohe[/B] - He ara ki te momo kōnae XML ahakoa kei runga i te taputapu, i te whatunga paetata ranei; [B]Ara Mamao[/B] - He URL e tohu ana i te waahi o nga momo momo konae XML."

#. help: Advanced - udpxyHost
msgctxt "#30663"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mena ko [B]Path Local[/B] te waahi me whai ara tika tenei tautuhinga."

#. help: Advanced - udpxyPort
msgctxt "#30664"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mena ko te waahi ko [B]Ara Mamao[/B] me whai URL tika tenei tautuhinga."

#. help: Advanced - useInputstreamAdaptiveforHls
msgctxt "#30680"
msgid ""
msgstr "Tautuhinga matatau tae atu ki nga relay multicast, nga taonga roma etc."

#. help: Advanced - useFFmpegReconnect
msgctxt "#30681"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko nga awa maha (UDP/RTP) kaore e pai te mahi ki nga whatunga Wifi. Ka taea e te rere multicast te huri i te awa mai i te UDP/RTP multicast ki HTTP. Ma te whakaahei i tenei kowhiringa ka huri i nga URL rerenga maha mai i te konae M3U ki nga wahitau HTTP kia taea ai te uru atu ma te rei 'udpxy' i te whatunga paetata. E.g. he URL rerenga maha UDP penei i te 'udp://@239.239.3.38:5239' ka huri ki tetahi mea penei 'http://192.168.1.1:4000/udp/239.239.3.38:5239'."

#. help: Advanced - defaultUserAgent
msgctxt "#30682"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko te ingoa kaihautu, te wahitau ip ranei o te reera multicast (udpxy) i te whatunga paetata."

#. help: Advanced - defaultInputstream
msgctxt "#30683"
msgid ""
msgstr "Ko te tauranga o te relay multicast (udpxy) i runga i te whatunga paetata."

#. help: Advanced - defaultMimeType
msgctxt "#30684"
msgid ""
msgstr "Whakamahia te inputstream.adaptive hei utu mo te libavformat a ffmpeg mo nga awa m3u8 (HLS)."

#. help: Groups - groups
msgctxt "#30685"
msgid ""
msgstr "Kia mahara ka taea anake te whakamahi ki nga awa http/https e tukatukahia ana e te libavformat (hei tauira M3u8/HLS). Ma te whakamahi i te libavformat ka taea te tautuhi i roto i te konae M3U ma te tautuhi i te taonga `inputstream` hei `inputstream.ffmpeg` mo te whakatinanatanga o roto o kodi, `inputstream.ffmpegdirect` ranei mo te putanga taapiri. I.e. te taapiri i te raina: `#KODIPROP:inputstream=inputstream.ffmpeg`. Ki te kore tenei kowhiringa e whakahohea ka taea tonutia ia awa/ hongere ma te taapiri i tetahi taonga kodi, ara: `#KODIPROP:http-reconnect=true`."

#. label: General - satipAutoConfig
msgctxt "#30686"
msgid ""
msgstr "Whakamahia tenei Kaiwhakamahi-Kaiwhakamahi mena kaore he mea i tukuna hei rawa, hei waahanga ranei o te URL awa hongere."

#. help: General - satipAutoConfig
msgctxt "#30687"
msgid ""
msgstr "Whakamahia tenei urungaream hei taunoa mena karekau he mea i tukuna hei taonga (KODIPROP) o te hongere. Whakamahia ma te tupato i te mea ka whakakorehia e tenei te whakamahi i te whanonga tirotiro awa taunoa a te addon. Kia mahara mo `inputstream.ffmpegdirect` ki te kore te `mimetype` me te `inputstream.ffmpegdirect.manifest_type` e kore e tautuhia ka haere tonu te tirotiro i te awa mena ka hiahiatia."

#. label: General - satipServerHost
msgctxt "#30688"
msgid ""
msgstr "Whakamahia tenei momo MIME hei taunoa mena karekau he mea i tukuna hei taonga (KODIPROP) o te hongere. Whakamahia ma te tupato i te mea ka whakakorehia e tenei te whakamahi i te whanonga tirotiro awa taunoa a te addon."

#. help: General - satipServerHost
msgctxt "#30743"
msgid ""
msgstr "Tautuhinga mo te whakarite i nga roopu hongere."

#. label: General - satipPreferFritzHd
